      "title": "Cheapest Cell Phone Plans For You!",
      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>Cheapest Cell Phone Plans For You!</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<p>We've got the most affordable phone plans under $40 for you. Whether you need unlimited data or just the bare minimum, we can help you find the perfect plan to keep your monthly costs low and your phone well-connected. Let's explore them together!</p>\n<img alt=\"Cheapest Cell Phone Plans For You!_1\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/cheapest-cell-phone-plans-for-you/cheapest-cell-phone-plans-for-you_1.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/cheapest-cell-phone-plans-for-you/cheapest-cell-phone-plans-for-you_1.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/cheapest-cell-phone-plans-for-you/cheapest-cell-phone-plans-for-you_1.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/cheapest-cell-phone-plans-for-you/cheapest-cell-phone-plans-for-you_1.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n</img></div>"
    },
    {
      "page": 2,
      "title": "Cheapest Cell Phone Plans For You!",
      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>Cheapest Cell Phone Plans For You!</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<h4>1. Mint Mobile</h4>\n<p>Mint plans start at just $15 per month, offering 5GB of data. Once you exceed 5GB, data will slow to 128 Kbps. The overall price is quite affordable, and you get access to T-Mobile's network, including 5G coverage. You can also make free calls to Canada and Mexico. However, to enjoy this attractive rate, you must pay for a full year of service after the first three months.</p>\n<img alt=\"Cheapest Cell Phone Plans For You!_2\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/cheapest-cell-phone-plans-for-you/cheapest-cell-phone-plans-for-you_2.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/cheapest-cell-phone-plans-for-you/cheapest-cell-phone-plans-for-you_2.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/cheapest-cell-phone-plans-for-you/cheapest-cell-phone-plans-for-you_2.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/cheapest-cell-phone-plans-for-you/cheapest-cell-phone-plans-for-you_2.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n</img></div>"
