      "title": "Cheapest Cell Phone Plans For You!",
      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>Cheapest Cell Phone Plans For You!</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<h4>4. T-Mobile</h4>\n<p>T-Mobile offers a $15 per month plan that includes 5GB data and 5G coverage. However, keep in mind that taxes and fees are not included. Once you hit the 5GB limit, you won’t have any more data until the next cycle. Additionally, the annual data boost will end in 2025.</p>\n<img alt=\"Cheapest Cell Phone Plans For You!_5\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/cheapest-cell-phone-plans-for-you/cheapest-cell-phone-plans-for-you_5.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/cheapest-cell-phone-plans-for-you/cheapest-cell-phone-plans-for-you_5.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/cheapest-cell-phone-plans-for-you/cheapest-cell-phone-plans-for-you_5.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/cheapest-cell-phone-plans-for-you/cheapest-cell-phone-plans-for-you_5.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n</img></div>"
