      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>Cheapest Cell Phone Plans For You!</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<h4>5. AT&amp;T</h4>\n<p>With AT&amp;T's plan, you pay $300 upfront, which averages out to just $25 a month for unlimited data. Plus, you get 10GB of hotspot data included. However, if you go over 16GB, your speed will drop to 1.5 Mbps. Despite this, it's hard to beat such a great monthly price.</p>\n<img alt=\"Cheapest Cell Phone Plans For You!_6\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/cheapest-cell-phone-plans-for-you/cheapest-cell-phone-plans-for-you_6.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/cheapest-cell-phone-plans-for-you/cheapest-cell-phone-plans-for-you_6.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/cheapest-cell-phone-plans-for-you/cheapest-cell-phone-plans-for-you_6.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/cheapest-cell-phone-plans-for-you/cheapest-cell-phone-plans-for-you_6.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n</img></div>"
